      "stem": "方程 $3x+1=7$ 的解是（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$x=2$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$x=\\frac{7}{3}$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$x=\\frac{8}{3}$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$x=6$" }
      ],
      "answer": "A",
      "analysis": "移项得 $3x=7-1=6$，系数化为1得 $x=2$。"
    },
    {
      "type": "choice",
      "id": "ex-14-02",
      "stem": "解方程 $2(x-1)=x+3$ 时，去括号正确的是（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$2x-1=x+3$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$2x-2=x+3$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$2x+2=x+3$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$2x-2=x-3$" }
      ],
      "answer": "B",
      "analysis": "去括号时，括号前是2，要乘以括号内的每一项：$2(x-1)=2x-2$，右边不变。"
    },
