        { "label": "A", "text": "5" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "8" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "10" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "12" }
      ],
      "answer": "C",
      "analysis": "由 $2x+3=5$ 得 $2x=2$，所以 $x=1$。则 $4x+6=4\\times1+6=10$。"
